title: The Blackstock Pub
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, Italian, Beer/Wine, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Located at 大阪府大阪市福島区福島7-1-10 OK2番街. Vegan choices are marked, could get the peperoncino with avocado and shiso leaf pasta, tomato sauce pasta, ratatoulle, pickled veggies, guacamole and salsa, edamame, olives, and mixed nuts. The other vegetarian dishes contain dairy and/or egg. Bar opens til 1am.
